aa(lp258
VSo here's the pitch:
p259
aVI think it's important that we don't just get on this freeway
p260
aVto ICU without thinking hard about whether or not
p261
aVthat's where we all want to end up,
p262
aVparticularly as we become older and increasingly frail
p263
aVand ICU has less and less and less to offer us.
p264
aVThere has to be a little side road
p265
aVoff there for people who don't want to go on that track.
p266
aVAnd I have one small idea,
p267
aVand one big idea about what could happen.
