aa(lp269
VAnd this is the small idea.
p270
aVThe small idea is, let's all of us
p271
aVengage more with this in the way that Jason has illustrated.
p272
aVWhy can't we have these kinds of conversations
p273
aVwith our own elders
p274
aVand people who might be approaching this?
